cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.CL, cs.CY

The paper deals with predicting the popularity of news stories, which involves information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (ML) techniques. Therefore, cs.IR and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper uses social network metadata and content-based features, which fall under the categories of social computing (cs.SI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper also deals with experimentation and measurement, which could be classified under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
